active.description: Controls the active state of the item. This is typically used to highlight the component.
active.description_zh: 控制项的活动状态。这通常用于突出显示组件。

allowed-dates.description: Restricts which dates can be selected.

bg-color.description: Applies specified color to the control’s background. Used on components that also support the color prop. - supports utility colors (for example success or purple) or css color (#033 or rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)). Find a list of built-in classes on the colors page.
bg-color.description_zh: 将指定的颜色应用于控件的背景。用于还支持颜色道具的组件。- 支持实用程序颜色（例如 success 或紫色）或 CSS 颜色（#033 或 rgba（255， 0， 0， 0.5））。在颜色页面上查找内置类的列表。

border.description: Designates the border-radius applied to the component. This can be xs, sm, md, lg, xl.
border.description_zh: 指定应用于组件的边框半径。这可以是 xs、sm、md、lg、xl。

color.description: Applies specified color to the control - supports utility colors (for example success or purple) or css color (#033 or rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)). Find a list of built-in classes on the colors page.
color.description_zh: 将指定的颜色应用于控件 - 支持实用程序颜色（例如 success 或紫色）或 css 颜色（#033 或 rgba（255， 0， 0， 0.5））。在颜色页面上查找内置类的列表。

disabled.description: Removes the ability to click or target the component.
disabled.description_zh: 删除了单击组件或将组件定位的功能。

display-value.description: The value that determines the month to show. This is different from modelValue, which determines the selected value.
display-value.description_zh: 确定要显示的月份的值。这与 modelValue 不同，modelValue 确定所选值。

elevation.description: Designates an elevation applied to the component between 0 and 24. You can find more information on the elevation page.
elevation.description_zh: 指定应用于组件的高程介于 0 和 24 之间。您可以在高程页面上找到更多信息。

header.description: Text shown when no display-date is set.
header.description_zh: 未设置显示日期时显示的文本。

height.description: Sets the height for the component.

hide-weekdays.description: Hide the days of the week letters.

landscape.description: Puts the picker into landscape mode.
landscape.description_zh: 将选取器置于横向模式。

location.description: Specifies the component’s location. Can combine by using a space separated string.
location.description_zh: 指定组件的位置。可以使用空格分隔的字符串进行组合。

max.description_zh: 允许的最大日期/月份（ISO 8601 格式）。

max-height.description: Sets the maximum height for the component.

max-width.description: Sets the maximum width for the component.

min.description_zh: 允许的最小日期/月份（ISO 8601 格式）。

min-height.description: Sets the minimum height for the component.

min-width.description: Sets the minimum width for the component.

mode-icon.description: Icon displayed next to the current month and year, toggles year selection when clicked.
mode-icon.description_zh: 图标显示在当前月份和年份旁边，单击时切换年份选择。

v-model.description: The v-model value of the component. If component supports the multiple prop, this defaults to an empty array.
v-model.description_zh: 组件的 v 模型值。如果组件支持多 prop，则默认为空数组。

month.description: The current month number to show
month.description_zh: 要显示的当前月份编号

multiple.description: Allow the selection of multiple dates. The range value selects all dates between two selections.
multiple.description_zh: 允许选择多个日期。范围值选择两个选择之间的所有日期。

next-icon.description: Sets the icon for next month/year button.
next-icon.description_zh: 设置下个月/下一年按钮的图标。

position.description: Sets the position for the component.

prev-icon.description: Sets the icon for previous month/year button.
prev-icon.description_zh: 设置上月/上年按钮的图标。

reverse-transition.description: The transition used when changing months into the past
reverse-transition.description_zh: 将月份更改为过去时使用的过渡

rounded.description: Designates the border-radius applied to the component. This can be 0, xs, sm, true, lg, xl, pill, circle, and shaped. Find more information on available border radius classes on the Border Radius page.
rounded.description_zh: 指定应用于组件的边框半径。这可以是 0、xs、sm、true、lg、xl、pill、circle 和 shaped。有关可用边框半径类的详细信息，请访问边框半径页面。

show-adjacent-months.description: Toggles visibility of days from previous and next months.
show-adjacent-months.description_zh: 切换上个月和下个月的天数可见性。

show-week.description: Toggles visibility of the week numbers in the body of the calendar.
show-week.description_zh: 在日历正文中切换周数的可见性。

tag.description: Specify a custom tag used on the root element.
tag.description_zh: 指定用于根元素的自定义标记。

text.description: Specify content text for the component.

theme.description: Specify a theme for this component and all of its children.
theme.description_zh: 为此组件及其所有子组件指定主题。

tile.description: Removes any applied border-radius from the component.
tile.description_zh: 从元件中移除任何应用的边框半径。

title.description: Specify a title text for the component.

transition.description: The transition used when changing months into the future
transition.description_zh: 将月份更改为未来月份时使用的过渡

view-mode.description: Determines which picker in the date or month picker is being displayed. Allowed values: 'month', 'months', 'year'.
view-mode.description_zh: 确定在日期或月份选取器中显示哪个选取器。允许的值：'month'、'months'、'year'。

weekdays.description: An array of weekdays to display.

weeks-in-month.description: A dynamic number of weeks in a month will grow and shrink depending on how many days are in the month. A static number always shows 7 weeks.
weeks-in-month.description_zh: 一个月中的动态周数将根据当月的天数而增长和减少。静态数字始终显示 7 周。

:year.description: The current year number to show
:year.description_zh: 要显示的当前年份编号

events.name: update:modelValue
events.description: Event that is emitted when the component’s model changes.
events.description_zh: 组件模型更改时发出的事件。

events.name: update:month
events.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

events.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

events.name: update:year
events.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

slots.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

slots.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

slots.description: Slot for the component’s title content.
